2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] ### Walker (`@shardworks/walker-apparatus`) — new package
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] 
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] **Data model:**
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - `RigDoc` — rig document stored in Stacks (`walker/rigs` book) with indexes on `status`, `writId`, `[status, writId]`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - `EngineInstance` — engine slot with `id`, `designId`, `status`, `upstream[]`, `givensSpec`, and optional `yields`/`sessionId`/`error`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] 
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] **Walk logic (collect > run > spawn priority):**
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - **Collect** — scans running engines with `sessionId`s; reads `animator/sessions` for terminal status; populates yields or fails engine
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - **Run** — finds the first pending engine with all upstream completed; calls `fabricator.getEngineDesign()` → `design.run()`; clockwork stores yields inline, quick stores `sessionId` and marks engine `running`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - **Spawn** — finds oldest ready writ with no existing rig; creates 5-engine pipeline; calls `clerk.transition(writId, 'active')`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] 
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] **CDC on `rigs` book (Phase 1 cascade):** rig `completed` → `clerk.transition(writId, 'completed', { resolution })`, rig `failed` → `clerk.transition(writId, 'failed', { resolution })`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] 
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] **Engines contributed via `supportKit.engines`:**
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - `draft` (real) — opens draft via Scriptorium, returns `DraftYields`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - `seal` (real) — seals draft via Scriptorium using `context.upstream['draft']`, returns `SealYields`
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] - `implement`, `review`, `revise` (stubs) — return hardcoded completed yields
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] 
2026-04-02T22:38:20Z [anima] **Tools:** `walk` (single step) and `walkContinual` (polling loop with configurable idle exit)
